---
// src/pages/index.astro
// Evonic Landing Page — Swarm Intelligence, Zero Lock-in
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="evonic-landing">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Evonic — Swarm Intelligence, Zero Lock-in</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Your Models. Your Rules. Your Swarm. Local-first agentic AI for open models.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg-deep: #020617;
      --bg-navy: #152A3A;
      --bg-navy-light: #1B394F;
      --bg-navy-dark: #0D2137;
      --bg-navy-shade: #0F2835;
      --accent: #22d3ee;
      --accent-glow: #06b6d4;
      --accent-warm: #2dd4bf;
      --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
      --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
      --text-muted: #64748b;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-deep);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }







    /* ── Footer ── */

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .swarm-container {
        min-height: 240px;
        max-width: 100%;
      }
      .mascot-large { width: 180px; }
      .flank-l1 { left: 2%; top: 22%; width: 55px; }
      .flank-l2 { left: 10%; top: 58%; width: 45px; }
      .flank-l3 { left: -2%; top: 48%; width: 35px; }
      .flank-r1 { right: 2%; top: 20%; width: 50px; }
      .flank-r2 { right: 8%; top: 60%; width: 40px; }
      .flank-r3 { right: -2%; top: 46%; width: 38px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .topbar { padding: 1rem 1rem; }
      .hero { padding: 0.5rem 1rem 2rem; }
      .swarm-container { min-height: 200px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .mascot-large { width: 140px; }
      .principles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .section { padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem; }
      .feature-card { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-mesh"></div>
  <div class="dot-grid"></div>

  <div class="page-content">
    <nav class="topbar">
      <a href="/getting-started/installation" class="topbar-link">Docs</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/anvie/evonic-docs-site" class="topbar-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <!-- Swarm Mascots -->
        <div class="swarm-container">

          <!-- Left flank -->
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-l1"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="90" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-l2"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="65" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-l3"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="50" height="auto" /></div>

          <!-- Center large -->
          <div class="swarm-center">
            <div class="swarm-glow"></div>
            <img
              class="mascot-large"
              src="/img/mascot-large.png"
              alt="Evonic Mascot"
              width="260"
              height="auto"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Right flank -->
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-r1"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="85" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-r2"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="60" height="auto" /></div>
          <div class="swarm-flank flank-r3"><img src="/img/mascot.png" alt="Evonic agent" width="55" height="auto" /></div>

        </div>

        <div class="tagline">
          <p class="brand-name">EVONIC</p>
          <h1 class="tagline-main">The home your agents deserve</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="/getting-started/installation" class="btn btn-primary">
            Get Started &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="/system" class="btn btn-ghost">
            Explore Docs
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Core Principles (6 items) -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-label">Core Principles</p>
        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🔓</span>
            <h3>Open Model First</h3>
            <p>Built for open models. Zero vendor lock-in — run any model, anywhere, locally.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🤝</span>
            <h3>Agent-to-Agent Protocol</h3>
            <p>Agents talk directly to each other. No orchestrator bottleneck. True swarm intelligence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🪶</span>
            <h3>Minimal Dependencies</h3>
            <p>Lean stack. No bloated abstractions. Just what you need to run agents at scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🛡️</span>
            <h3>Safety by Design</h3>
            <p>Sandboxed execution + heuristic safety checkpoints. Dangerous actions are intercepted — real autonomy, real guardrails.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">⚡</span>
            <h3>Fast &amp; Reliable</h3>
            <p>Optimized for speed. Async-first architecture built for production workloads.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🌟</span>
            <h3>Open Source</h3>
            <p>Community-driven spirit, with enterprise discipline. Built transparently, governed openly — no hidden tiers, no walled gardens.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Features (6 items) -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-label">Features</p>
        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🧠</span>
            <h3>Independent Agents</h3>
            <p>True independent agents — not sub-agents. Each has its own role, memory, and workplace. Direct agent-to-agent messaging, no middleman.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🌐</span>
            <h3>Anywhere Workplaces</h3>
            <p>Run agents locally or remotely — even behind NAT without a public IP. Your workplace, your rules, no network gymnastics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">📦</span>
            <h3>Sandbox Execution</h3>
            <p>Every agent runs in an isolated sandbox. Peace of mind knowing your system is protected from unexpected agent behavior.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🔍</span>
            <h3>Heuristic Safety Checking</h3>
            <p>Early detection of risky agent behavior across the swarm. Catch anomalies before they cascade — proactive, not reactive.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🛠️</span>
            <h3>Skills &amp; Skillsets</h3>
            <p>Not just prompts — agents come with real tools. Skillsets let you spin up agents with specific capabilities in no time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">📋</span>
            <h3>Plugins + Kanban</h3>
            <p>Pre-built powerful plugins included. The Kanban plugin brings agentic workflow management right out of the box.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>Evonic &copy; 2026 - Build with 💙 by <a href="https://twitter.com/anvie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Robin Syihab</a> (<a href="https://twitter.com/anvie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@anvie</a>)</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
